---
// CostRunaway.astro — Pure CSS animated cost meter
// Shows how token costs spiral when a loop doesn't terminate properly
---

<div class="cr-wrap">
  <h3 class="cr-title">The Cost Spiral — When Loops Don't Stop</h3>
  <p class="cr-sub">A single runaway loop burned $47 in 3 minutes. Here's exactly how.</p>

  <div class="cr-layout">
    <!-- The cost ticker -->
    <div class="cr-ticker">
      <div class="cr-meter-label">Token Cost (live)</div>
      <div class="cr-meter">
        <div class="cr-meter-bar">
          <div class="cr-meter-fill cr-meter-fill--safe" style="--w:8%"></div>
          <div class="cr-meter-fill cr-meter-fill--warn" style="--w:28%"></div>
          <div class="cr-meter-fill cr-meter-fill--danger" style="--w:65%"></div>
          <div class="cr-meter-fill cr-meter-fill--critical" style="--w:100%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-meter-markers">
          <span class="cr-marker cr-marker--safe">$0.02<br/><small>normal</small></span>
          <span class="cr-marker cr-marker--warn">$0.80<br/><small>high</small></span>
          <span class="cr-marker cr-marker--danger">$12<br/><small>alert</small></span>
          <span class="cr-marker cr-marker--critical">$47<br/><small>killed</small></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Loop-by-loop cost table -->
      <div class="cr-table">
        <div class="cr-row cr-row--header">
          <span>Iteration</span><span>Tokens</span><span>Cost</span><span>Cumulative</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row" style="--d:0.2s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 1</span><span class="cr-tok">1,840</span><span>$0.02</span><span class="cr-cum">$0.02</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row" style="--d:0.3s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 2</span><span class="cr-tok">3,200</span><span>$0.04</span><span class="cr-cum">$0.06</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row" style="--d:0.4s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 3</span><span class="cr-tok">5,100</span><span>$0.08</span><span class="cr-cum">$0.14</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row cr-row--warn" style="--d:0.5s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 5</span><span class="cr-tok">12,400</span><span>$0.22</span><span class="cr-cum cr-cum--warn">$0.80</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row cr-row--danger" style="--d:0.7s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 12</span><span class="cr-tok">68,000</span><span>$3.20</span><span class="cr-cum cr-cum--danger">$12.40</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row cr-row--critical" style="--d:0.9s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 23</span><span class="cr-tok">210,000</span><span>$18.50</span><span class="cr-cum cr-cum--critical">$47.20</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cr-row cr-row--killed" style="--d:1.1s">
          <span class="cr-iter">Loop 24</span><span class="cr-tok">—</span><span>—</span><span class="cr-cum cr-cum--killed">⛔ KILLED</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why it happened -->
    <div class="cr-why">
      <div class="cr-why-title">What Went Wrong</div>

      <div class="cr-cause">
        <div class="cr-cause-num">1</div>
        <div class="cr-cause-content">
          <div class="cr-cause-name">Context window snowball</div>
          <div class="cr-cause-desc">Each loop appended the full result to the context. By loop 12, the agent was re-reading 68K tokens of its own history just to make one decision.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cr-cause">
        <div class="cr-cause-num">2</div>
        <div class="cr-cause-content">
          <div class="cr-cause-name">No exit condition</div>
          <div class="cr-cause-desc">The agent's "am I done?" check was an LLM call too — which hallucinated "more work to do" because the prompt was too long to parse correctly.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cr-cause">
        <div class="cr-cause-num">3</div>
        <div class="cr-cause-content">
          <div class="cr-cause-name">No budget guardrail</div>
          <div class="cr-cause-desc">There was no per-run spending cap. The kill switch was a human checking Slack — 3 minutes too late.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cr-fix">
        <div class="cr-fix-icon">🛡</div>
        <div>
          <strong>The fix:</strong> Hard cap at 8 iterations. Sliding context window (keep last 2 loops only). Per-run budget limit of $0.50 with auto-halt.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .cr-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .cr-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .cr-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .cr-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .cr-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* Ticker */
  .cr-ticker {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .cr-meter-label { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cr-meter { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .cr-meter-bar {
    height: 16px; background: #1e293b; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;
  }
  .cr-meter-fill {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; height: 100%;
    width: 0; animation: cr-fill 2s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .cr-meter-fill--safe     { background: #4ade80; z-index: 4; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .cr-meter-fill--warn     { background: #f59e0b; z-index: 3; animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .cr-meter-fill--danger   { background: #ef4444; z-index: 2; animation-delay: 1.0s; }
  .cr-meter-fill--critical { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #dc2626); z-index: 1; animation-delay: 1.4s; }
  @keyframes cr-fill { to { width: var(--w); } }

  .cr-meter-markers {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .cr-marker {
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; text-align: center; line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .cr-marker small { color: #475569; font-size: 0.45rem; }
  .cr-marker--safe { color: #4ade80; }
  .cr-marker--warn { color: #f59e0b; }
  .cr-marker--danger { color: #ef4444; }
  .cr-marker--critical { color: #dc2626; }

  /* Table */
  .cr-table { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .cr-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 0.8fr 1fr;
    padding: 5px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; color: #94a3b8;
    animation: cr-row-in 0.4s ease-out both; animation-delay: var(--d, 0s);
  }
  .cr-row--header {
    color: #64748b; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #334155; animation: none;
  }
  .cr-row--warn { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.04); }
  .cr-row--danger { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.04); }
  .cr-row--critical { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.08); }
  .cr-row--killed { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.12); }
  @keyframes cr-row-in { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(4px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  .cr-iter { color: #64748b; }
  .cr-tok { color: #94a3b8; }
  .cr-cum { color: #4ade80; }
  .cr-cum--warn { color: #f59e0b; }
  .cr-cum--danger { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 700; }
  .cr-cum--critical { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 700; }
  .cr-cum--killed { color: #f87171; font-weight: 700; }

  /* Why */
  .cr-why {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .cr-why-title { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700; }

  .cr-cause {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .cr-cause-num {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700;
    background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); color: #f87171; border: 1px solid #ef444430;
  }
  .cr-cause-name { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .cr-cause-desc { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.5; }

  .cr-fix {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; margin-top: 14px;
    padding: 10px 14px; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.15); border-radius: 10px;
    color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .cr-fix strong { color: #4ade80; }
  .cr-fix-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
</style>
